@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ubeufo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v1
    v2 = wp.abs((v0 - wp.abs(v1 + 0.94)))
    tmp = v0
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.98 * tmp + 0.22) + (v1 + 0.43 - v1 + 0.88)) * wp.cos(0.29))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
